HEADWORD: Disquietly
<hw>Dis*qui"et*ly</hw>, <pos>adv.</pos> <def>In a disquiet manner;
uneasily; <as>as, he rested <ex>disquietly</ex> that night</as>.</def>
<mark>[R.]</mark> <rj><au>Wiseman.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
